Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我们已经抵达3号转向点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have reached projected point 3, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,设定新航道，方位201坐标15\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Adjust to new course 2-0-1 mark 1-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医生，她情况怎么样了？ - 不大好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How is she, doctor? - No change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真得感谢星际舰队！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Small thanks to the Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,协调员，这事儿怪不得星际舰队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now really, commissioner, you can't blame the Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来应该提前接种防疫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I should have received the proper inoculations ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,樱花病是一种极其罕见的病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sakuro's disease is extremely rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,感染这种病的机率差不多是十亿分之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The chances of anyone contracting it are literally billions to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大夫，我被派往埃普西隆卡纳瑞三号阻止战争冲突\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was sent to Epsilon Canaris III to prevent a war, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,托星际舰队医疗分部行事拖沓的福\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks to the inefficiency of the medical branch of the Starfleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在工作完全做好之前我就被迫提早回程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been forced to leave before my job was done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,协调员，我向你保证，一旦我们回到进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commissioner, I assure you that once we reach the Enterprise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,使用她先进的医疗设备，我们绝对能够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with its medical facilities, we'll have you back to your job
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,使你尽快返回你的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in time for you to prevent that war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我们什么时候才能到你的飞船呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How soon will we rendezvous with that ship of yours, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,协调员，只需要4小时21分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In exactly four hours, 21 minutes, commissioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长 - 嗯？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你看一下自动扫描仪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will you check your automatic scanner, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？我以前从来没有见过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's odd. I've never seen anything like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nor have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它正以曲速向我们飞来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Heading directly toward us at warp speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,它好像故意堵在我们的航道上 史波克先生，扫描器读数？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's staying right with us. Sensor readings, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是由一团氢离子构成的云层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vaguely like a cloud of ionized hydrogen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是发出强烈的电磁脉冲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but with strong erratic electrical impulses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们撞上它了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长，方向舵不听使唤了 - 太空梭失去控制了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Helm does not answer, captain. - Neither do the pods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,与外界的通讯中断，电路超载，切断所有电力中继\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Communications are dead. Building overload. Cut all power relays.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,已切断，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cut, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，到底怎么了，快告诉我！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, what's happening? I demand to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哈特福德女士，我们知道的不比你多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You already know as much as we do, Miss Hedford.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不管外面是个什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever that thing is outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,总之它使我们偏离了既定航道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it yanked us off course from the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在的方位是98坐标12，直冲伽马卡纳瑞区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now on course 9-8 mark 1-2, heading directly toward Gamma Canaris region.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我们必须把哈特福德女士带回进取号！她的病情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim. We've got to get Miss Hedford back to the Enterprise. Her condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，老骨头，但是现在只能听天由命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know, Bones. But there's nothing I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须马上返回与进取号会合的航道上！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I insist you make your scheduled rendezvous with the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哈特福德女士，我们已尽力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miss Hedford, we'll do what we can when we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,目前这种情况，我们孤立无援\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the moment, we're helpless. You might as well sit back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你也只能好好坐稳而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and enjoy the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，终极的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,去发现新的世界和新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilisations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00DA4E&}-=THE LAST FANTASY=-\N荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：多宝大如来\N校对：喜马拉雅{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,第二季第九集\N「变形生物」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号，这里是伽利略号太空梭，请回话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise, this is the Galileo. Come in, please. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号，这里是伽利略号太空梭，请回话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise, this is the Galileo. Come in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,情况不妙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,信号根本发不出去，老骨头?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not transmitting. Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,氮氧环境，还有少许氪，氩，氖等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oxygen-nitrogen atmosphere, some krypton, argon, neon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,温度为华氏75度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Temperature, 75 degrees Fahrenheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎完全等同于地球的大气环境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Practically identical to Earth's atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克？ - 重力和地球一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Spock? - Gravity similar to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,根据星球的体积，这种重力很不寻常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Most unusual, in view of its size.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,星球的主体部分主要由铁元素和镍元素组成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The bulk of the body seems to be iron and nickel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,比起陨星来更接近小行星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More than an asteroid, like a small planetoid, I should say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能是一颗行星解体后的碎片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}possibly a remnant from a planet breakup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,完全适合人类生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Totally suitable for human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，咱们出去瞧瞧，把相位枪准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, we get out and get under. Issue phasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，保持高度警惕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, maintain full alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,协调员，您先在这里休息一会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commissioner, if you'll stay inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我应该休息多久呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just how long am I supposed to stay inside, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好问题！我也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's a very good question. I wish I could answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好，走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，四处探查一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take a look around, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太不寻常了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Most unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不太可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我得说极其不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In fact, captain, I would say quite impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 机器没有任何故障但就是不工作 - 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Nothing wrong and nothing works. - Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 肯定有什么原因 - 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- There must be a reason. - Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再好好检查一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's look a little further.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我刚刚用三录仪扫描了一下周边环境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, I just took a tricorder sweep, and I got the exact same readings
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,读数和太空梭刚偏离航道时的读数几乎一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}almost as Spock got when we were pulled off course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 离子云？ - 我觉得是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The ionized cloud? - I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只是这次离子云读数在星球表面，就在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only it reads here on the surface with us. It's off in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而且读数显示其不是固体，非常不稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it doesn't read solid. It's more unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,像是一团稀薄的气体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tenuous, like a collection of gases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，读取一下那人的生理信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, get a physiological reading on that, whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是真实的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you real?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是，你们不是我幻想出来的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, I'm not imagining you, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对真实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're real enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你会讲英语？是地球人吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You speak English. Earth people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来自星际联邦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,星际\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The F...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，管他呢，我叫寇可兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, it doesn't matter. I'm Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道我被困在这里待了多久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been marooned here who knows how long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你们我实在太高兴了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you only knew how good it is to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,见到女人我更高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还是一个大美女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A beautiful one at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是进取号舰长詹姆士·寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm Captain James T. Kirk, commanding the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是我的大副史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is my first officer, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是瓦肯人吧？ - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You're a Vulcan, aren't you? - Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,首席医官伦纳得·麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Chief Surgeon Leonard McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大夫 - 幸会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Doctor. - Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,星联助理委员哈特福德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And excuse me, Assistant Federation Commissioner Hedford.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真是雪中送炭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Food to a starving man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都是我的炭火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，这艘船真不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, that's a nice ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来风格简约又干净\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Simple and clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,打算修好它吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Been trying to get her to go again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我看还是省省吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forget it. It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他的各项生理读数都说他是一个地球人，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's human, Jim. Everything checks out perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是被一股神秘的力量强行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were forced off our course...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,拖离航道到这里来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and taken here by some force we couldn't identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这股力量我们无法分析，所以不知道来自何方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which seems to be on the surface of this body at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wouldn't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚说我们无法使这艘太空梭再度运行吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You say we'll be unable to get the ship to function again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行 这里有某种阻尼场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not a chance. There's some sort of damping field down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,动力系统都无法工作，相信我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Power systems don't work. Take my word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会继续尝试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't mind if we continue to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以，随你便，反正你们有的是时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go right ahead. You've got plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生，谈谈你的情况吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about you, Cochrane?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么到这儿来的呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚不是说了吗，落难在此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Marooned. I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们要是想聊天的话有的是时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, we'll have lots of time to learn about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小屋就在那个方向上，一起去坐坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have a small place over that way. All the comforts of home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以洗个热水澡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can even offer you a hot bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真有眼力，我很想马上就洗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How perceptive of you to notice that I needed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生，您说得实在太笼统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you don't mind, Mr. Cochrane, I'd like a little more than just a statement
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这里离航路很远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that you were marooned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,您是怎么落难的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a long way off the beaten path.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,说得对，所以我看见你们才这么高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's right. That's why I'm so glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你们一切，但是这儿说话不方便\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I'll tell you everything you want to know. But not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们的太空船真是太漂亮了 - 那是自然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Your ship is sure a beauty. - Yes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你现在也已经闭锁了一段时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you've been out of circulation quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很多原理你可能以前从来没有听说过，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The principles may be new to you. Mr. Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,给寇可兰先生讲解一下推动器工作原理吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...why don't you explain our methods of propulsion to Mr. Cochrane?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他虽然话多，但是有用的说得不多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He talks a lot, but he doesn't say much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 而且我还注意到一些其他东西 - 是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I've noticed something else. - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他看上去很面熟 - 面熟？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He looks familiar. - Familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,经你这么一说，我也觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now that you mention it, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我一时想不起来在哪里见过他，但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't quite place him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哈特福德女士的情况怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about Miss Hedford?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,目前还没发烧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No temperature yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是事情耽搁不得，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we've got to get underway soon, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢保证她马上就会有严重的症状了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I guarantee you it will develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,到那时我们该怎么办？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,先去寇可兰那坐坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take Cochrane up on his offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生，你自己建的这个？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You built this, Mr. Cochrane?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，我的小船坠毁前装着必要的工具和材料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. I had tools and supplies left over from my crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还不赖，虽说不如地球上的舒服，但起码能住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not bad. Not Earth, of course, but it's liveable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我在那边的小山丘上种植了一些蔬菜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I grow vegetables in the fields over that next ridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,简直就像家那样舒适\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the comforts of home, indeed, Mr. Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪弄的这些老古董？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where did you get the antiques?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说这些仪器？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean my instruments?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜外面的世界一定变化了很多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I imagine things have changed a lot since I crashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,其实变化也不算太大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:11:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你这里怎么这么热？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Must you keep it so terribly hot in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,温度一直保持在华氏72度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The temperature is a constant 72 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喝点冷饮吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me get you something cool to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得很热吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you feel hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得心里有火，无处宣泄！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I feel infuriated, deeply put upon, and absolutely outraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,走这么久你肯定累了，先休息一会儿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was quite a hike here. You're tired. Just take it easy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我一会儿就休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll rest later, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经开始出现症状了，感觉热是第一个征兆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Temperature, captain. First sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们时间不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I know. It means we're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain. Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候光线会造成奇特的光影效果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sometimes the light plays tricks on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时候在光线的刺激下也会产生幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'd be surprised what I've imagined I've seen around here sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生，那绝不是幻觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We imagined nothing, Mr. Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有个实实在在存在的东西，刚刚就在外边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was an entity out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀疑刚才那怪光和把我们带到这里的 离子云有联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I suspect it was the same entity which brought us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,请解释一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么可说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's nothing to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你，当我的船员切身安全受到威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll find I have a very low tolerance level
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我的脾气是很不好的！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where the safety of my people are concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你独自一人生活在这个荒无人烟的地方 而且拒绝透露有用的信息！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We find you here where no human has any business being.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们突然在太空中遇险最后流落到这么个地方！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were virtually hijacked in space and brought here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在不是请求你给我们一个解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not just requesting an explanation, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我在要求一个解释！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm demanding one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 它叫做“伴随实体” - 什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It was the Companion. - The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我给它取的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's what I call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上我的船并非坠毁于此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As a matter of fact, captain, I didn't crash here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是被带到这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was brought here in my disabled ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我已经奄奄一息了，“伴随实体”救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was almost dead. The Companion saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你当时受伤了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，我当时奄奄一息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was dying, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在看起来很健康，怎么回事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You seem perfectly all right now. What was the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那时我已经是个老头子了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚是怎么回事，但是“伴随者”把我返老还童了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know how it did it, but the Companion rejuvenated me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我从一个老头子又变成了一个小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}made me young again, like I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你的这个故事持保留意见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I prefer to reserve judgement on that part of your story, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,同时，你能不能给我解释一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Meanwhile, would you please explain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你的这个伴随者到底是什么东西？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}exactly what this Companion of yours is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说过了，我也不知道，它存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told you, I don't know what it is. It exists,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它是生命体，而且我还能跟它交流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it lives, and I can communicate with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这可真是一个奇异的故事 - 寇可兰先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- That's a pretty far-out story. - Mr. Cochrane...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名是什么？ - 杰佛瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...do you have a first name? - Zefram.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,杰佛瑞·寇可兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Zefram Cochrane...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来自半人马三星？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...of Alpha Centauri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 曲速引擎的发明者？ - 没错，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The discoverer of the space warp? - That's right, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这绝对不可能！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,杰佛瑞·寇可兰150年前就去世了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Zefram Cochrane died 150 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,杰佛瑞·寇可兰的名号响彻寰宇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The name of Zefram Cochrane is revered throughout the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有好多星球以他的名字命名，还有很多大学，城市等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Planets were named after him, great universities, cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生，您的故事着实不太可信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Isn't your story a little improbable, Mr. Cochrane?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的都是真的，我来到这里的时候已经87岁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, it's true. I was 87 years old when I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你说这个伴随者发现了你并且还让你返老还童\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You say this Companion found you and rejuvenated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你87岁的时候为什么还在太空里旅行？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What were you doing in space at the age of 87?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时身心俱疲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was tired, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,行将枯朽，我想死在太空里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was going to die, and I wanted to die in space. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,确实，他的尸体从来没有被找到过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}True, his body was never found.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，活生生的就站在你面前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're looking at it, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,果真如此，你的生理年龄被缩减了好多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If so, you wear your age very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你感觉怎么样了？ - 你说呢？我难受死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How do you feel? - Terrible. How should I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在有点发烧，最好躺下休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're running a little temperature. Perhaps you should lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，麻烦你离我远点，因为实在是太热了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, will you please just leave me alone? It's the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，尽量放松身心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right. Try to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始有症状了，是发烧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's started, the fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,已经超过100华氏度了，而且还在上升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's over 100, and it's climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还有多久？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,最多能挺几个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A matter of hours, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生，您说您在150年前就来到这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Cochrane, you say you were brought here 150 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我看您顶多35岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't look a day over 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者让我返老还童，并且一直保持 35岁的生理年龄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I haven't aged. The Companion sees to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这些设备，确实属于寇可兰的那个年代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These instruments, they date from the time indicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,都是你船上的吗，寇可兰先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From your ship, Mr. Cochrane?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我从船上拆下来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I cannibalized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,除了这些设备，我其他的生活需求 比如食物，水，花园\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The food, water, gardens, everything else I need,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,都是伴随者使用周围的物质给我创造的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the Companion gives me. Apparently creates it out of the native elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,您说您能跟它交流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You say you can communicate with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那您不妨问问它干嘛把我们带到这里来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps you can find out what we're doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我已经知道了 - 那您不打算告诉我们吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I already know. - You wouldn't mind telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我怕说了你不高兴 - 我已经很不高兴了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You won't like it. - I already don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来这里的主要目的就是做我的伙伴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're here to keep me company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是其实是你把我们带到这里来的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean you brought us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不，是伴随者带你们过来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, the Companion did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟伴随者说如果这样下去我会孤独至死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told it I'd die of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我本以为这样它就会放了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought it would release me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,结果它把你们带到这里来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Instead, it brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不！不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好恶心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又不是禽兽！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,简直是奇耻大辱！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, it's inhuman. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，使用三录仪收集更多的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, run additional tricorder readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,尽全力分析，争取能发明一种战胜它的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Learn anything you can. Find me a weapon to use against this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,武器？你想让我消灭它吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You ask me to find a weapon. Do you intend to destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果只有这样才能离开这个星球的话，是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I intend to do whatever is necessary to get us off this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,况且哈特福德女士的病也耽搁不得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and Commissioner Hedford to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要是伴随者挡路，那咱们就把它赶走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the Companion stands in the way, then we push it out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了，史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Clear, Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Quite clear, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好，忙你的去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very well. You have your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生，离开这儿会对你有影响吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Cochrane, if you left here, what would happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我的身体会重新进入正常老化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd begin to age again, normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那你想离开这里吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you want to leave here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你相信我，永生实在是太无聊了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Believe me, captain, immortality consists largely of boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,外面的银河系世界是什么样子的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's it like out there, in the galaxy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经探索的星球约有1000颗！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're on 1,000 planets and spreading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的星舰飞跃了你无法想象的距离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We cross fantastic distances
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,生命在银河系中遍地开花！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and everything's alive, Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们估计有上百万颗星球都有智慧生物生存！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Life everywhere. We estimate there are millions of planets with intelligent life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这些星球都在那里等着我们去探索！如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We haven't begun to map them. Interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得一颗已经沉睡了150年的心灵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How would you like to go to sleep for 150 years
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,突然苏醒在一个崭新的世界会怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and wake up in a new world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那些未知的新世界在那里等你去探索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's all out there waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们需要你的帮助才能离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we'll need your help to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定帮你们！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这个伴随者能够使用周围的元素制造出物体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You seem to think this Companion of yours can do almost anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,它确实有这个能耐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said it was very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那它能治好这位女士吗？ - 这我不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Could it cure her? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是如何跟它交流的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you communicate with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的交流类似于心电感应，属于非语言层面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's on a non-verbal level, but I usually get my message across.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:19:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须尝试跟它交流，这方面我们必须依靠你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got to try. We're helpless. See if it can do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么跟他交流的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,首先我要排除杂念，然后它自然会过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just sort of clear my mind, and it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，发表一下看法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, what do you make of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,像是某种共生关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Almost a symbiosis of some kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一种交和 - 我也是这么想的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- A sort of joining. - Exactly what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得二者的关系并不是主人和\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not exactly like a pet owner
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,宠物之间那样简单，你觉得呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}speaking to a beloved animal, would you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 绝对不止如此 - 我同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No, it's more than that. - Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,更像是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,爱情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有点消耗体力，不过没什么大碍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, it kind of drains me a little, but I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的事儿它答应吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者也无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Companion can't do anything to help Miss Hedford.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那哈特福德女士必死无疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then she'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我有办法，一定全力以赴去帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there's anything I could do to help, I would, and I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是伴随者是指望不上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we can expect nothing from the Companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？ - 大夫先生，我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Are you all right? - Yes. Quite all right, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了一件很有趣的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A most fascinating thing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显，伴随者将一种原始的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Apparently, the Companion imparted to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,高压电流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a rather quaint, old-fashioned electric shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,输入到我的身体里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...of respectable voltage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的意思是它袭击你了？ - 显而易见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It attacked you? - Evidently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,由此可知，它的身体中有一大部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unquestionably, a large part of its substance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,组织就是电流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...is simple electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，虽说我不是科学家或物理学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not a scientist or a physicist, Mr. Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.34,0:22:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我知道任何能够产生电流的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but am I correct in assuming that anything that generates electricity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,都能够短路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}can be shorted out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，你说得很对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Quite correct, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个仪器放在伴随者附近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put this in the proximity of the Companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只要按下这个开关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Throw this switch,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它就能够扰乱那个生物所制造的电流回路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and it will scramble every electrical impulse the creature can produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对错不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It cannot fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰，怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It troubles you, Cochrane?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Companion saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这么些年来是它一直照顾我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's taken care of me all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之间的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢？非常亲密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...very close in a way that's hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至对它有点难以启齿的依恋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I suppose I even have a sort of affection for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:22:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可是它同样也是囚禁你的罪魁祸首\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's also keeping you prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我不希望它被杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want it killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是暂时把它瘫痪而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We may simply render it powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.23,0:23:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你怎么保证呢？ 你有可能会杀掉它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you don't know. You could kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,柯克，这一点我绝无法容忍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't stand for that, Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生，我们需要离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're getting out of here, Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请面对现实！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Face up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我会不择手段地确保我手下人的生命安全！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll do anything I have to to save all of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,站在你的立场上讲，你确实没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I suppose, from your point of view, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生，我们能够理解你的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We understand how you feel, Mr. Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可是眼下我们别无它法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it has to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，要我出去引它出来吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right. Do you want me to contact it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,请一定帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please. Outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有句俗话怎么说来着？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What was it they used to call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,舍不得孩子套不着狼？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Judas goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，确实有一定危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is some risk, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们尚不清楚伴随者的能量究竟有多大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We do not know the extent of its powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它也不知道我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nor it ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.34,0:24:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,停止！你想杀了他们吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop it! You're killing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.54,0:25:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了，请停止，他们没法呼吸了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop it, please! Stop it! You're choking them!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.79,0:25:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,放了他们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.50,0:25:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们快憋死了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're choking them!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.25,0:25:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.11,0:25:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 吉姆，你还好吧？ - 还好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Are you all right, Jim? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.94,0:25:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克？ - 我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Spock? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.00,0:25:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰把它引过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cochrane got it off of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.71,0:25:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不知道这对我们算是好事还是坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I don't know whether he did us a favour or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.94,0:25:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你说这话是什么意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What kind of talk is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.20,0:25:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎么能斗得过那东西呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you fight a thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.17,0:25:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,做为一船之长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got a ship up there somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.84,0:26:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要为这里的四个性命负责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the responsibility of four lives down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.01,0:26:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们中的一个因为我的缘故就要死掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}one of them dying because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.12,0:26:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.18,0:26:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，我是舰长，舰长就是扛事儿的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm in command, Bones. It makes it my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.35,0:26:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎么能斗得过那样一个生命体呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you fight a thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.19,0:26:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了，武力从来就不是解决问题的首选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe you're a soldier so often
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.90,0:26:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不仅要学会做战士，更要懂得沟通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that you forget you're also trained to be a diplomat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.86,0:26:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,当大棒不顶用的时候，干嘛不试试胡罗卜？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why not try a carrot instead of a stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.62,0:26:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克 - 舰长，什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Spock. - Yes, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.63,0:26:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们的穿梭机里有宇宙翻译器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The universal translator on the shuttlecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.71,0:26:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们试试用那玩意儿和那个生物体沟通一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can try that, talk to that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.71,0:26:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙翻译器不是为这种生命形式设计的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The translator is for use with more congruent life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.38,0:26:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看看能不能调整一下，尝试和那个东西沟通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Adjust it. Change it. The trouble with immortality is it's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.22,0:26:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,况且还可以消磨这里无限的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Adjusting it will give you something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.14,0:26:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我有办法拓宽它的接收模式的话是有可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is possible. If I could widen its pattern of reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.68,0:26:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这项工作刚好能发挥你的天才，干吧史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right down your alley, Spock. Get it here and get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.23,0:26:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那个生物还在外面，你最好走那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And that thing is still out there. Better go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.19,0:27:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 情况怎么样了？ - 更糟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Any change? - Yes. For the worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.72,0:27:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰日志，星历3219.8.\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ship's log, stardate 3219. 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.43,0:27:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特少校于舰长不在舰时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Commander Scott
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.81,0:27:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,代理寇克舰长进行记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}recording in the absence of Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.98,0:27:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,载有寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A shuttlecraft, bearing the captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.31,0:27:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大副，首席医官麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the first officer, Chief Surgeon McCoy,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.94,0:27:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,星联助理协调员哈特福德女士的太空梭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and Assistant Federation Commissioner Hedford,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.94,0:27:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没能按计划时间与进取号会合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is now definitely overdue for a rendezvous with the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.78,0:27:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们目前正在尝试搜索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are attempting to backtrack it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.54,0:27:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.04,0:27:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,计算机中心报告说我们马上就要到达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Computer central reports that we are coming up on the coordinates
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.04,0:27:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太空梭失踪之前的最后一个坐标位置了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the last established position of the shuttlecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.00,0:27:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 稳定，史考特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Thank you, lieutenant. - Steady. No. Mr. Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.05,0:27:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,方位310坐标35已扫描未发现反物质残余\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bearing 3-10 mark 3-5 just cleared. No antimatter residue.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.59,0:27:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所有扫描器，执行球状搜索程序，最大范围\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All scanners, spherical sweep. Range, maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.60,0:27:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要找到他们！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll have to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.60,0:27:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要是太空梭本身已经失去动力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the shuttlecraft powered away, Mr. Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.31,0:27:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,单单靠惯性滑行怎么办？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if it were just towed?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.69,0:27:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是那样也会有蛛丝马迹的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There'd still be traces of residual matter floating around, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.19,0:28:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,方位210坐标40发现高浓度粒子聚集\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bearing 2-10 mark 4-0. Strong particle concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.28,0:28:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生，看来我们这回找对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're on it, Mr. Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.36,0:28:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,开始设置追踪航道，继续扫描\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lay on the course. Maintain scanning.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.87,0:28:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,航道已设置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Course laid in, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.42,0:28:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,粒子密度开始衰减了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Particle density decreasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.09,0:28:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,完全消散了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gone, sir. No readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.55,0:28:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁先生，保持航道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Steady as she goes, Mr. Sulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.35,0:28:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生，这意味着什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you think it means, Mr. Scott?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.35,0:28:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可以推知：至少五小时之前太空梭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The shuttlecraft was on schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.85,0:28:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一直保持在既定航道上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}until it was shy five hours of rendezvous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.02,0:28:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,然后出现了突发情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.07,0:28:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能再说得确定一些？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd feel a lot better if it were a little more definite.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.32,0:28:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何碎片残骸，所以太空梭至少不是被摧毁的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It didn't wreck. There was no debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.36,0:28:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没有发现氧气聚集现象，没有残余的放射性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no trace of expelled internal atmosphere. No residual radioactivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.58,0:28:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.70,0:28:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,被某个物体掳走了可能，是牵引光束一类的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something took over. Tractor beams, maybe. Something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.17,0:28:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那个什么东西就在这个地方把太空梭拖走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It dragged it away on the heading we're now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.42,0:29:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没有任何痕迹了，我们怎样搜寻他们呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if there are no further traces, how are we going to follow them?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.09,0:29:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就保持现在的航道，静观其变吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We stay on this course. See what comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.85,0:29:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可是银河系太大了，史考特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a big galaxy, Mr. Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.94,0:29:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,说得不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.19,0:29:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这个设备的工作原理是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the theory behind this device?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.49,0:29:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的智慧生物的思维模式都是大同小异的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are certain universal ideas and concepts common to all intelligent life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.28,0:29:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这台设备能够匹配讲话者的脑波频率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This device instantaneously compares the frequency of brainwave patterns,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.58,0:29:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然后辨识出这些频率分别代表的含义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}selects those ideas and concepts it recognises,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.08,0:29:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再用特定的语法将其组织起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then provides the necessary grammar.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.83,0:29:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如此一来就能把任何其他语言翻译成英语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then it simply translates its findings into English.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.46,0:29:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是这东西能讲话？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean, it speaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.96,0:29:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,它可以发出声音或者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With a voice or the approximation
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.76,0:29:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,用跟对方相似的方式交流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of whatever the creature is on the sending end.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.26,0:29:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是百分之百管用，不过凡事没有完美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not 100 percent efficient, of course, but nothing ever is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.05,0:29:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克先生，可以了吗？ - 可以了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Ready, Mr. Spock? - Quite ready, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.10,0:29:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Cochrane...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.43,0:29:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,把伴随者召唤出来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...call the Companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.44,0:30:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Companion...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.86,0:30:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想跟你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...we wish to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.32,0:30:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能和我沟通？难道你们能够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How can we communicate? My thoughts...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.62,0:30:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看见我的思维？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}... you are hearing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.00,0:31:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.88,0:31:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克，毫无疑问她是雌性 - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Feminine. No doubt about it, Spock. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.63,0:31:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这个生物体的性别对形势有关键影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The matter of gender could change the entire situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.26,0:31:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Way ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.63,0:31:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她的角色并非动物管理员 - 不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It is not a zookeeper. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.60,0:31:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,更像是一个爱人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.56,0:31:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Companion...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.69,0:31:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,违背我们的意愿而把我们囚禁在这里是不对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...it is wrong to keep us here against our will.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.24,0:31:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男人需要他自己的同类来陪伴他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Man needs the company of his own kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.37,0:31:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,否则他就会消亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or he will cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.91,0:31:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是这样告诉我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He felt it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.50,0:31:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不放我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One of us will cease to exist
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.96,0:31:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中的一个就会马上消亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if we don't get her to a place where we can care for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.92,0:31:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男人需要他的同类作伴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Man needs others of his species.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.13,0:31:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你们在此的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is why you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.76,0:31:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男人的生命必须得到延续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Man must continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.93,0:32:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者，你换位思考一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Companion, try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.52,0:32:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的种族天性就向往自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is the nature of our species
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.19,0:32:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就好比你的天性就是喜欢待在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to be free, just as it is your nature to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.36,0:32:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们被囚禁的话，我们会逐渐消亡的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will cease to exist in captivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.45,0:32:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们身体的自然老化程序已经被中止了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your bodies have stopped their peculiar degeneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.62,0:32:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们没什么好怕的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There will be nothing to harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.50,0:32:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会永恒存在，那个男人亦然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will continue, and the Man will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.17,0:32:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很合理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.97,0:32:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是拓展我们知识的千载难逢的好机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a marvellous opportunity to add to our knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.90,0:32:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以询问关于她的生理状态，她种族的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ask it about its nature, its history.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.83,0:32:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不是课堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This isn't a classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.08,0:32:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,现在首要任务是离开此处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm trying to get us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.99,0:32:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,以后可能没这种机会了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A chance like this may never come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.68,0:32:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们获取新知的绝好机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It could tell us so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.55,0:32:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不是干这个的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This isn't the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.95,0:32:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Companion...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.99,0:32:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你提供给我们的根本不是永恒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...what you offer us is not continuation,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.16,0:32:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而是停滞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it is nonexistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.75,0:33:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如此下去我们会消亡的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.08,0:33:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人同样也会消亡的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even the Man will cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.67,0:33:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的行为不合逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your impulses are illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.51,0:33:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这次交流纯属浪费时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This communication is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.18,0:33:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人必须保持存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Man must continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.55,0:33:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,由此，你们亦可保持存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Therefore, you will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.56,0:33:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这是必要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.30,0:33:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.84,0:33:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们干嘛把翻译器的音频输出设定为女性的声音？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...why did you build that translator with a feminine voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.47,0:33:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们没 - 但是我明明听见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We didn't. - But I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.01,0:34:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生，雄性和雌性是一种普遍区分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The idea of male and female are universal constants, Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.06,0:34:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者的性别无疑是女性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no doubt about it, the Companion is female.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.10,0:34:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不明白 - 你不明白？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I don't understand. - You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.69,0:34:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,瞎子都能看得出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A blind man could see it with a cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.78,0:34:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你并非宠物，也不是笼子里的标本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not a pet. You're not a specimen kept in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.37,0:34:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是她的配偶 - 我是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You're a lover. - I'm a what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.33,0:34:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她对待你的态度和她对待我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Her attitude when she approaches you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.20,0:34:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,态度是绝对不同的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is profoundly different than when she contacts us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.25,0:34:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,当她与你沟通时，态度温柔，优雅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Her appearance is soft, gentle,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.92,0:34:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她的声音有旋律，愉悦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}her voice is melodic, pleasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.34,0:34:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然缺体验情绪的经验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do not totally understand the emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.23,0:34:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我能确定这些不同是存在的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it obviously exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.18,0:34:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Companion loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.64,0:34:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么呀？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.13,0:34:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这么些年来，某些非常怪异的感觉在我体内游移不去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For all these years I've let something as alien as that crawl around inside me,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.06,0:34:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我无法摆脱，听凭其行 - 这一点上你无权抱怨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- into my mind, my feelings. - What are you complaining about?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.69,0:34:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 毕竟是她让你活下来的 - 那玩意饲养我，消遣我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It kept you alive, didn't it? - That thing fed on me, used me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.49,0:34:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得这样很恶心 - 根本没什么值得恶心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It's disgusting. - There's nothing disgusting about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.28,0:34:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,它只不过是不同于我们的一种生命体而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's just another life form, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.34,0:35:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你的思维被旧观念限定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You get used to those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.12,0:35:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法赞同你！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're as bad as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.12,0:35:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你目前的这种夸张的情绪反应很不符合逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your highly emotional reaction is most illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.96,0:35:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你和伴随者的这种关系已经维持了150年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your relationship with the Companion has for 150 years
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.29,0:35:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,从这种关系中可以发掘出情绪上的满足，实用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}been emotionally satisfying, eminently practical,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.63,0:35:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而且完全没有副作用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and totally harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.42,0:35:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要说这种关系 是非常符合你的个人利益的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It may indeed have been quite beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.76,0:35:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,原来未来一切以利益为先？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this what the future holds?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.22,0:35:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,人们完全无视尊严和道德？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Men who have no notion of decency or morality?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.48,0:35:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我已经落伍了150年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe I'm 150 years out of style,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.56,0:35:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我绝对不会当外星怪胎的宠物！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I'm not going to be fodder for any inhuman monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.49,0:35:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很有趣非常狭隘的观念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fascinating. A totally parochial attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.49,0:35:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.66,0:35:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.84,0:35:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在，哈特福德女士 - 我刚刚听到他说的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Right here, Miss Hedford. - I heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.38,0:35:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他被那个生命体所爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.93,0:36:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他却对这种爱全然厌恶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and he resents it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.85,0:36:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你做梦了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You just rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.06,0:36:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.65,0:36:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.03,0:36:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我事业有成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been good at my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.16,0:36:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.74,0:36:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有被爱过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...l've never been loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.08,0:36:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一次也没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.54,0:36:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那是怎样的日子吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What kind of life is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.46,0:36:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道从来没有被爱过是什么感觉吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not to be loved?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.63,0:36:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至对别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Never...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.47,0:36:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,示爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...to have shown love.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.19,0:36:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他唯一做的就是逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And he runs away from love.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.04,0:37:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰日志，星历3220.3.\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ship's log, stardate 3220.3.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.96,0:37:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Commander Scott reporting
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.63,0:37:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,代替舰长和大副进行记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in lieu of the captain and the first officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.88,0:37:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们仍旧在搜索失踪的太空梭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are continuing our search for the missing shuttlecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.43,0:37:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，接近了一个小行星带\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Approaching what seems to be an asteroid belt, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.93,0:37:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,扫描器显示大约有7000个小行星体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scanners report approximately 7,000 bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.60,0:37:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 其体积大致分布于A型至M型 - 大气读数呢?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- of sizes running from types A to M. - Atmosphere count?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.98,0:37:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大约有百分之三十四的小行星体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Approximately 34 percent of the bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.40,0:37:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,含有从H型至M型的大气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have atmosphere in types H to M.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.98,0:37:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，现在我们就用最笨的办法搜索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right then. We do it the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.03,0:37:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所有感应器设置为扫描生命体，自动筛选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All sensors set for life-form registration. Automatic selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.28,0:37:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生，如果说他们就在其中一颗小行星上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Scott, there are thousands of them out there they could be on,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.61,0:37:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们的搜索范围可是上千颗小行星呀！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if they're on any of them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.28,0:37:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对，中尉，上千颗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's right, lieutenant. Thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.67,0:37:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们只能一颗一颗地找\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we'll look them over, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.63,0:37:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者，你爱那个男人吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Companion, do you love the Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.88,0:38:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I... do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.14,0:38:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他对你很重要吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is he important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.64,0:38:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他对于你来说是不是比任何东西都重要？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More important than anything. Is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.90,0:38:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像他是你身体的一部分似的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As though he were a part of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.59,0:38:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是我的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He is part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.86,0:38:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人必须要持续下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Man must continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.78,0:38:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会持续存在下去的，他会逐渐消亡的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He will not continue. He will cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.28,0:38:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然从你的角度看是为了他好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By your feeling for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.24,0:38:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你所谓的这种善意却让他感觉窒息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you're condemning him to an existence he will find unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.25,0:38:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他会逐渐消亡的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He will cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.54,0:38:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可是他从此不老不死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He does not age. He remains forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.12,0:38:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不老不死的只是他的肉体而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You speak of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.96,0:38:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我强调的是他的灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I speak of his spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.18,0:38:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者，就在那间小房子里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Companion, inside the shelter,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.01,0:38:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一个女性已经病入膏肓了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a female of our species is dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.52,0:38:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,按你的话说，她马上就要停止持续了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She will not continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.81,0:38:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不放我们走，我们都会停止持续的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is what will happen to the Man unless you release all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.23,0:39:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法理解你的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.61,0:39:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的种族，只有在不断地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our species can only survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.37,0:39:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,征服各种困难中才能使灵魂延续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...if we have obstacles to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.66,0:39:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而你直接把所有的困难都清除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You take away all obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.75,0:39:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有困难，我们就没办法使自己变强\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Without them to strengthen us,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.71,0:39:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的生命由此会最终枯竭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we will weaken and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.55,0:39:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你只不过是把那个男人当成玩物而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You regard the Man only as a toy. You amuse yourself with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.68,0:39:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大错特错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.35,0:39:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人是整个宇宙中最重要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Man is the centre of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.35,0:39:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我珍视他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I care for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.06,0:39:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你并没有爱的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you can't really love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.11,0:39:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你对人类的爱情没有丝毫的了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't the slightest knowledge of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.42,0:39:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,爱情是同类之间才会有的一种关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the total union of two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.53,0:39:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而你是伴随者，而他是人类！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are the Companion. He is the Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.74,0:39:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是完全不同的两个物种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are two different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.99,0:39:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你们之间没办法真正的交合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't join.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.75,0:40:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不懂什么是真正的爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.92,0:40:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你虽然能把他的肉体永远困囚于此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You may keep him here forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.05,0:40:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是实际上，你们的灵魂之间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...but you will always be separate...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.97,0:40:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,却永远隔绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...apart from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.27,0:40:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是人类的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I were human...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.94,0:40:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是否就可以懂得爱了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}... there can be love?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.42,0:40:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，你刚刚说的那番话是为了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What did you hope to gain by that, Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.47,0:40:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想劝说她放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Try to convince her of the hopelessness of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.80,0:40:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有些时候，爱就意味着放手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Love sometimes expresses itself in sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.89,0:41:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为能让她明白真爱要学会放手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought maybe if she loved him, she'd let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.44,0:41:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她，或说它，并不是人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But she, or it, is inhuman, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.52,0:41:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能指望她像人类那样去做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You cannot expect her to react like a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.32,0:41:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我试过了 - 没用的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I tried. - It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.45,0:41:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.24,0:41:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,杰佛瑞·寇可兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Zefram Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.61,0:41:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.65,0:41:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚是怎么回事，她的病痊愈了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't understand it. She's not sick at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.78,0:41:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.78,0:41:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.04,0:41:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.29,0:41:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白吗？伴随者附体了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you understand? It's the Companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.04,0:41:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.54,0:41:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在完全健康，一切生命体征都正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's perfectly healthy. Heart like a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.25,0:41:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸正常，血压正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Respiration, normal. Blood pressure, normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.17,0:41:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这在医学上是不可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is medically impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.26,0:41:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们就是证据 - 你说我们？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We are here. - We?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.51,0:41:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.06,0:42:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是协调员和伴随者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those you knew as the commissioner and the Companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.10,0:42:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们合成了一个意识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are both here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.10,0:42:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随者，你应该没有创造生命的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Companion, you do not have the power to create life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.53,0:42:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那是上帝的领域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is for the maker of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.02,0:42:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是哈特福德女士已经奄奄一息了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But Commissioner Hedford was dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.66,0:42:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意识中哈特福德那部分已经十分虚弱了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That part of us was too weak to hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.70,0:42:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在某一刻，她几乎要停止延续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In a moment, there would have been no continuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.88,0:42:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现在我们在一起了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now we're together.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.00,0:42:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你和伴随者共处在一个躯体里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you are both here in the one body?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.34,0:42:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们合二为一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.52,0:42:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,杰佛瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Zefram.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.94,0:42:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们吓到你了吗？你过去从来不怕我们啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We frighten you. We've never frightened you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.37,0:43:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.21,0:43:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这种感觉是孤独吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.46,0:43:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,天那，多么痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, what a bitter thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.13,0:43:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，杰佛瑞，太不幸了这些年 你是如何承受这种孤独感的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, Zefram, it's so sad. How do you bear it, this loneliness?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.35,0:43:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，检查一下太空梭，引擎，通讯什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, check out the shuttlecraft. Engine, communications, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.48,0:43:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，没有必要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That will not be necessary, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.15,0:43:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的太空梭已经能够正常运作了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your vehicle will operate as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.80,0:43:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,包括通讯系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So will the communications device.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.03,0:43:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你同意让我们走了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're letting us go?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.41,0:43:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今我们也无法阻止你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We could do nothing now to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.41,0:43:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾经说过，因为我们不是人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said we would not know love
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.31,0:43:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们无法真正第理解人类的爱情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because we were not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.79,0:43:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们是人类了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now we are human.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.49,0:43:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们理解了世间的沧桑变化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll know the change of the days.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.92,0:43:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也理解了死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will know death.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.35,0:44:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是当我拉住那男人的手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But to touch the hand of the Man
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.78,0:44:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我依旧觉得，没有什么比他更重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}nothing is as important.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.22,0:44:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你长得非常美丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.06,0:44:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的部分人格明白你说的话，部分却不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Part of me understands. Part does not.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.53,0:44:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是我就是爱听 - 我可以详细为你解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- But it pleases me. - I could explain. Many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.16,0:44:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，杰佛瑞，我们一起去散步吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, let me walk, Zefram.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.62,0:44:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,让我体验一下土地轻触双脚的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me feel the earth against my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.29,0:44:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,让我体验一下阳光洒在面颊的温暖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me feel the warmth of the sun on my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.38,0:44:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你陪在我身边，我们一起去体验这些美好的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You beside me. Let me feel these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.59,0:44:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧，寇可兰，我们这边还有事要忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go ahead, Cochrane. We have a few things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.99,0:45:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生，接收到舰长的信号了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Scott, it's the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.24,0:45:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,接通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.62,0:45:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,锁定他的坐标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lock onto his coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.33,0:45:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我是史考特，你们没事吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, this is Scotty. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.58,0:45:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没事，你们能锁定我们吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perfectly all right. Can you get a fix on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.50,0:45:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,舵手正在计算你们所处的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The helm is computing your position now, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.71,0:45:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,方位224，坐标12\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Course 2-24 mark 1-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.97,0:45:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,地球标准时，57分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}ETA, 57 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.55,0:45:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们大约于57分钟之后可到达你们的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll be there in 57 minutes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.72,0:45:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，我会一直保持通讯畅通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very good. I'll continue transmitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.77,0:45:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦到达指定位置马上进入标准轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Assume standard orbit when you arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.09,0:45:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会乘坐太空梭回舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll transport up in the shuttlecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.04,0:45:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你们到底发生了什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happened, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.86,0:45:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,说来话长，史考特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Interesting story, Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.98,0:45:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我一时和你说不清楚，况且，说老实话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't tell you now, because, quite frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.90,0:45:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不知道结局会如何，寇克完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know how it's going to end. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.11,0:45:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,外面的任何一件事都会让你大开眼界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything will be an eye-opener to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.03,0:45:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有上千颗有生命的星球，上千个种族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's 1,000 planets out there, 1,000 races.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.91,0:45:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到了外面的世界后，一旦我学习得 差不多了，我也会向你逐一展示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I'll show everything to you as soon as I learn my way around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.79,0:45:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我还可以做些事，来回馈你这些年为我做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe I can make up a little for everything you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.93,0:46:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,杰佛瑞，我不能和你一起走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't go with you, Zefram.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.11,0:46:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然能跟我走，而且你必须跟我一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course you can. You have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.81,0:46:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的生命起源于此处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My life emanates from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.60,0:46:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我离开这里，我就会停止延续的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I should leave it for more than a tiny march of days, I'll cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.74,0:46:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要回来，就如同你们必须要消耗 物质来维持生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must return, even as you must consume matter to maintain your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.16,0:46:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是说如果你要成为人类 就意味着失去你原有的一切？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean you gave up everything to be human?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.92,0:46:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，即使你留在这里，你最终还是会死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But even if you stay here, you'll eventually die.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.79,0:46:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,起码此时此刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The joy of this hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.84,0:46:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我很快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.97,0:46:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能把你扔在这里自己走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I can't just fly away and leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.22,0:46:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,杰佛瑞寇可兰，你一定要得到自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must be free, Zefram Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.84,0:46:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是你救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.48,0:46:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你照料我，而且还爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You took care of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.77,0:46:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我却从来没有理解你的爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and you loved me. I never understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.69,0:47:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我现在全都明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.50,0:47:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经进入标准轨道并且锁定了你们的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're locked in, captain. Standard orbit established.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.26,0:47:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太空梭停泊港随时准备接收你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shuttlecraft Bay standing by to receive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.63,0:47:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特，待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand by, Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.10,0:47:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,寇可兰先生，进取号就在轨道上等我们上去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Enterprise is waiting, Mr. Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.73,0:47:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕我不能带她走了，一旦她离开这里就会死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't take her away from here. If I do, she'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.90,0:47:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我抛下她，她也会死于孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I leave her, she'll die of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.57,0:47:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我此生已经亏欠她太多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I owe everything to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.20,0:47:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能就这么抛下她自己走，我爱她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't leave her. I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.86,0:47:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我这么说吓到你们了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.03,0:47:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,从一个地球人嘴里说出这话，我一点不惊异\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not coming from a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.16,0:47:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟你们原本就是不理性的种族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are, after all, essentially irrational.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.33,0:47:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想想吧，寇可兰先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Think it over, Mr. Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.50,0:48:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,外面整个银河系都以你为荣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a whole galaxy out there waiting to honour you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.42,0:48:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我有她就足够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have honours enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.04,0:48:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你们两个即使在这里也会继续衰老的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you will age, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.47,0:48:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不会永生不死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There will be no immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.68,0:48:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会逐渐地衰老最后死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll both grow old here and finally die.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.60,0:48:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,千百年来人们不一直都是这样的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's been happening to men and women for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.85,0:48:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是和她一起白头偕老\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got the feeling it's one of the pleasanter things about being human,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.35,0:48:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这也不失为一件乐事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as long as you grow old together.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.78,0:48:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿定主意了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.15,0:48:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这里水源充足气候也很适宜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's plenty of water here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.61,0:48:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,种植食物没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The climate is good for growing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.41,0:48:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我将来还打算种植一些无花果树\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I might even try and plant a fig tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.78,0:48:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,男人自古以来不就是播种者吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A man's entitled to that, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.16,0:48:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在说的都是心理话，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It isn't gratitude, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.62,0:48:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我看着她，触摸她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now that I see her, touch her...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.09,0:48:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我爱她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I know that I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.58,0:48:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里会很幸福地生活在一起的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll have a lot of years together, and they'll be happy ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.72,0:48:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你万事顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.60,0:48:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，还有一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.31,0:49:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,别把我的事情告诉别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't tell them about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.19,0:49:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保守秘密的，寇可兰先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not a word, Mr. Cochrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.24,0:49:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.16,0:49:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,埃普西隆卡纳瑞三号星上的战争怎么办？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about that war on Epsilon Canaris III?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.66,0:49:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信星际联邦会另外找到一位有能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sure the Federation can find another woman somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.02,0:49:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止战争的女士的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who'll stop that war.
